{"type": "article", "id": 3709, "title": "可以从中间拧开的ALEX Bottle", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-20T07:43:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233205qDS76VTKfbociPwM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自加州 Carlsbad 的设计团队 ALEX Bottle 日前推出了一款同名的水瓶，其名字寓意永远活得非凡「Always Live Extraordinarily」。平日里我们携带外出的水瓶，总是会遭遇瓶身过长、瓶口太细而不方便清洗的问题，而这款 ALEX Bottle 却可以从中间拧开，使得使用者可以轻松地清洗瓶身内部地各种茶渍、咖啡渍等。当然，唯一需要提防地是不要在瓶内装满液体的时候将其拧开哦。目前，ALEX Bottle 正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1914152870/alex-bottle-twist-open-clean-easy-pack-small\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter </a>上众筹，起售价 26 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/800/316/14d4a55f978543472d2c1c5aaea25067_large.gif?1414264736\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233203fxzEFkBnVbyGdCj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233204tPqTNsGzOJf0veiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332042vFC9HxT6ukdJ8ir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233204GA8VgURdneEi2Jxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233205MIp8tly6EDnsoFkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}